Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
+ Industrial, office or retail possibilities
+ Located in desirable Butterfield Business Center with over 100 companies
+ No City sales tax
+ Great freeway access – within ½ mile

Seven Individual Lots
• Build-to-suit land parcels
• City of Tucson I-1 zoning
• Across the street and next to several new projects including FedEx Ground Facility (±210,000 SF), Old Dominion Truck Terminal, HomeGoods Western US Distribution Center (±850,000 SF) and a ±158,000 SF speculative building by Harsch Property Investment Properties.
• Infrastructure in place (subject to distribution from Elvira Road):
- Electricity
- Water & sewer
- Telecom
- Gas

Three 2-ton overhead cranes, air compressors and several pipe racks included. Fully fenced property. Natural gas service. Currently occupied and owned by a steel fabrication business. List of equipment and tools available upon request.
